3.Check palindrome.

s="madam"
if "".join(reversed(s))==s:
    print("palindrome")
else:
    print("not palindrome")
o/p-->palindrome
Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(n)



#optimized approach-->

se="ayushi"
right=len(se)-1
left=0

while(left<right):
    if(se[left]!=se[right]):
        print("not palindrome")
        break
    left+=1
    right-=1
else:
        print("palindrome")

o/p-->not palindrome
Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
